data.description: This barely lived in home (built 2022) is ready for you to move into today!  With 5 beds, 3 full bathrooms, this home offers a functional and spacious floor plan and lots of natural lighting.  Thoughtful upgrades include vinyl fence, backsplash in kitchen, renovated pantry, added bathroom storage, epoxy flooring in garage, garage door opener, updated faucets and fixtures throughout. Stainless steel kitchen appliances and washer/dryer included.  Tile in all the main living areas.  On the lower level, you'll find one bed and a full bathroom.  Make your way upstairs to find the remaining 4 bedrooms, including the oversized owners suite.  Owner's suite features large walk-in closets and ensuite bathroom with walk-in shower and dual vanity sinks.  Equipped with smart home technology.  Tile flooring in main living areas.  Enjoy all that this incredible location at COURTLAND PARK has to offer including direct access to the Land-to-Sea Loop Trails, Minutes from Downtown Sanford.  Approximately 30 minutes drive to the Beautiful Beaches of Florida and only a 35 min drive to Orlando for an easy commute. Nearby schools, Take a look and feel the comfort.  Make this home yours today!
